sentences.english: In this paper one decision method of normal function is given.
sentences.chinese: 給出了一個全純函數爲正規函數的判定方法。

sentences.english: Some criteria for normality of families of holomorphic functions with one shared-value are studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究涉及一個分擔值的全純函數族的正規定則。

sentences.english: In this article holomorphic curves in the complex hyperbolic space are discussed.
sentences.chinese: 研究復雙曲空間中的全純曲線。
